353
00:23:16,465 --> 00:23:18,850
<i>Alasanku bergaul
dengan orang-orang bodoh ini?</i>

354
00:23:19,176 --> 00:23:20,685
<i>Anak Kepala Jaksa.</i>

355
00:23:21,261 --> 00:23:23,063
<i>Anak pemilik perusahaan tekstil.</i>

356
00:23:23,972 --> 00:23:25,690
