aku bisa bersantai sebentar.

397
00:26:38,166 --> 00:26:39,667
Kau baik sekali.

398
00:26:39,668 --> 00:26:42,420
Kau ingin minum apa? Aku traktir hari ini.

399
00:26:42,421 --> 00:26:45,256
- Benarkah? Kalau begitu aku...
- Hei.

400
00:26:45,257 --> 00:26:47,225
Kau harus bayar.

401
00:26:47,843 --> 00:26:50,603
