414
00:27:49,863 --> 00:27:51,289
Kapan?

415
00:27:51,698 --> 00:27:55,293
Kau selalu coba mendekatiku saat sekolah.

416
00:27:55,702 --> 00:27:57,212
Sekarang pun begitu.

417
00:27:59,956 --> 00:28:02,509
Apa kau bilang? Kau mabuk?

418
00:28:05,087 --> 00:28:07,555
Tidak. Aku asal bicara.

419
00:28:09,257 --> 00:28:11,643
Kau selalu bilang tidak apa.

420
00:28:12,219 --> 00:28:15,522
Kalau dilihat lucu juga,
kau tak pernah mengajakku berpacaran.

421
00:28:18,058 --> 00:28:19,859
Apa kau hanya bermain-main?

422
