438
00:29:30,005 --> 00:29:31,181
Ayo main lagi.

439
00:29:31,756 --> 00:29:34,008
Ada jalan besar kalau aku lewat sini.

440
00:29:34,009 --> 00:29:35,852
Aku bisa dapat taksi di sana.

441
00:29:36,678 --> 00:29:38,438
Kenapa kau tiba-tiba pergi?

442
00:29:38,638 --> 00:29:40,398
Apa karena kau tak suka aku?

443
00:29:43,268 --> 00:29:44,694
Ya.

444
00:29:45,395 --> 00:29:46,571
Kenapa?

445
00:29:46,813 --> 00:29:48,782
Kenapa kau tak suka denganku?

446
00:29:49,816 --> 00:29:52,902
Wajah, cara bicara, suaramu.

447
00:29:52,903 --> 00:29:55,654
Bola mata, gigimu, bulu matamu,

448
00:29:55,655 --> 00:29:57,540
bola matamu...

449
00:29:57,866 --> 00:29:59,167
Itu sudah kusebutkan?

450
00:30:00,368 --> 00:30:02,337
Aku tak suka semuanya darimu.

451
00:30:03,205 --> 00:30:04,547
Aku pergi dulu.

452
00:30:07,417 --> 00:30:08,843
